{"tid":1587570,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先係西貢排van仔出旺角個位絲打","createTime":"2019-09-22T12:44:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T13:05:09.000Z","uid":17019,"like":3,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4106d2c4ed76aa635ef66da3750300939b95366f","tid":1587570,"uid":17019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T12:44:38.000Z","msg":"灰短髮紮辮<br />\n著綠色露腰衫<br />\n黑色牛仔牌<br />\n白色Stan smith<br />\nPrada背囊<br />\n<br />\n我排係你後面個位白帽男<br />\n頭先如果問你拎聯絡方法會好突兀<br />\n我知你有上連登架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到個po留言相認啊<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"1f475dcd8ee9cd6829e80737a8d6951772b79272","tid":1587570,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T12:44:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9b42fe4075d27034911df2cbfb60854d689637b","tid":1587570,"uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T12:46:39.000Z","msg":"收皮啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"f3fb475dbc8ad956a5ea4b1692fa55c8c5b1049f","tid":1587570,"uid":45772,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T12:47:37.000Z","msg":"收皮啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"41b06b28e7b284b8b05f7564367a210f8e776c13","tid":1587570,"uid":34676,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T12:47:45.000Z","msg":"樓主好嘔心"},{"pid":"7c6a85f8e45c7c2b0972f0eb85fe5b8f36fa16e4","tid":1587570,"uid":259373,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T12:47:51.000Z","msg":"你咁樣係唔會溝到女㗎"},{"pid":"23c9e5b897207982bcd7731440a74b089c4c4f5b","tid":1587570,"uid":205482,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T12:48:09.000Z","msg":"reported!<br />\n樓豬自己反省下"},{"pid":"77203fdabb21a87e7acda6c6649d404cc7b57761","tid":1587570,"uid":110200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T12:48:27.000Z","msg":"善用不推文回覆啦"},{"pid":"ec371abd8369485503e7cd841966cd231596a4a5","tid":1587570,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T12:50:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樹窿再次歡迎大家加入<br />\n知道過去兩個月，大家既生活都過得好壓抑。有人係依兩個月之間同父母嗌大交，同伴侶分手，同朋友斷交，有人晚晚夜歸，有人用到無哂錢。或者你覺得好迷惘好無奈，或者你覺得無岀路。有見及此，開左個谷俾大家入黎吐下苦水，只談現實，不談夢境。希望大家可以舒發下，減減壓，然後大家一齊繼續向前行。<br />\n<br />\n發緊想發未發就發夢都唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不要質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/E2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FE2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBs2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=b0cc4cd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/E2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外就係<br />\n過去個兩個月正正常常係比應屆DSE同學仔溫書休息既<br />\n可惜呢個政府搞到大家奉獻左成個暑假，為左自己又好，為左將來又好，為左下一代又好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前有見連登上有多個關於網上問功課谷既需求，有見及此就有呢個DSE支援服務。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，免費網上問功課谷一直以唔張揚嘅方法存在。谷內有十多位Tutors (當中包括現職老師及名校畢業生在讀生)同DSE同學仔。形式係以分科細谷你問我答為主，亦有提供簡單練習同改文服務。同學亦可以問升學選科等問題。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一直隱姓埋名係為左保障學生安全。但見到需求增加，又多左好多不同既補習post。所以我地希望提供俾同學多一個安全安心既選擇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如有同學有需要，請聯絡：<br />\nTG: mama612<br />\n(暫時有足夠Tutor所以暫不接受更多tutor)<br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3bfcf55c08a7d0d603a775bcd7574e84149b874","tid":1587570,"uid":167878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T12:51:01.000Z","msg":"躝啦"},{"pid":"1c2e101868e26aafcd5077f49615d8cc6fa0a5ec","tid":1587570,"uid":42304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T12:52:48.000Z","msg":"死狗公，原來係你"},{"pid":"90cbdec3ed02ab7b000a83cd6c797bfdc766b2eb","tid":1587570,"uid":250356,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:05:09.000Z","msg":"樓主 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 變態！！！"}]}